# ✉️ Email Writer - React Frontend  

## 🚀 Introduction  
The **Email Writer React App** is a web-based application that helps users generate AI-powered email drafts quickly and efficiently. This frontend interacts with the backend to provide seamless email composition, suggestions, and customization.

## 🛠 Installation  

Follow these steps to set up and run the project on your local machine:  

1️⃣ **Clone the Repository**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/surya-vempa/Email-Assistant.git

2️⃣ Navigate to the Project Directory
bash
Copy
Edit
cd Email-Assistant/email-writer-react

3️⃣ Install Dependencies
Make sure you have Node.js (v20+) installed. Then, install project dependencies:

bash
Copy
Edit
npm install

4️⃣ Run the Development Server
bash
Copy
Edit
npm run dev
This will start the React application on http://localhost:5173/ (Vite default port).

